abstract: >
  AnimalTaskSim provides hybrid DDM + LSTM agents trained to reproduce
  psychometric, chronometric, and sequential-history fingerprints observed
  in macaque and mouse decision-making tasks.  The project bridges classical
  drift-diffusion modeling with recurrent policy learning, enabling stochastic
  reaction-time dynamics and cross-species behavioral calibration.
